                </p>    
              </div>
              <div class="px-6 pt-4 pb-2">
                <span class="inline-block bg-gray-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mr-2 mb-2">#todo</span>
                <span class="inline-block bg-gray-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mr-2 mb-2">#todo</span>
                <span class="inline-block bg-gray-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mr-2 mb-2">#tododododu</span>  
              </div>
            </div>
             <!-- divider -->
            <div class="max-w-sm rounded overflow-hidden shadow-lg m-4">
              <img class="w-full" src="/img/weather.jpg" alt="Sunset in the mountains">
              <div class="px-6 py-4">
                <div class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Weather forecast</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-base">
                  <span class="text-green-500">Given</span> I have opened main page<br />
                  <span class="text-green-500">When</span> I press weather forecast menu element<br />
                  <span class="text-green-500">Then</span> weather forecast page is oppened<br />
                  <span class="text-green-500">When</span>I change show items to 5<br />
                  <span class="text-green-500">And</span> Press Change button<br />
                  <span class="text-green-500">Then</span> table show 5 rows with data<br />
                </p>    
              </div>
              <div class="px-6 pt-4 pb-2">
                <span class="inline-block bg-gray-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mr-2 mb-2">#sunny</span>
                <span class="inline-block bg-gray-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mr-2 mb-2">#cloudy</span>
                <span class="inline-block bg-gray-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mr-2 mb-2">#seesharpy</span>  
              </div>
            </div>
